snippet.title: Let's Play Star Trek Online - Midnight
snippet.description:
Hello Captains, it is finally here, the last and final Star Trek Online mission to end the Iconian war and storyline.  "Midnight" wraps up the Iconian storyline that has been built in STO for over 5 years.  It culminates the entire storyline and puts a "The End" on its tail.  Will it add up?  Can it overcome the hype?  Let's find out.

Yes, this video is long, but worth it.  Stay tuned at the end for I will try on the new Iconian Vest and look at the rewards and then give my review and summary of the mission at the end.

-Brent
